videos.description: Dupree McBrayer seems to have a wide-open layup, but Nick Ward ranges over to smack a layup off the backboard to close out the first half.
videos.headline: Ward swats McBrayer to end first half

videos.description: Xavier Tillman picks off the pass and Cassius Winston leads the fast break, dropping a behind-the-back pass to Nick Ward for the big finish.
videos.headline: Winston goes behind-the-back to Ward for dunk

videos.description: Amir Coffey races down the court and takes off for the rim, throwing down a nasty one-handed jam all over Matt McQuaid.
videos.headline: Coffey posterizes McQuaid
